<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="866">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$meng-ban-yu-sheng" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/meng-ban-yu-sheng" class="zg-link" title="梦伴余生">梦伴余生</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$liu-bai-ke-lian-zi-geng" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/liu-bai-ke-lian-zi-geng" class="zg-link" title="六百克莲子羹">六百克莲子羹</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$he-gan-ming-44" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/he-gan-ming-44" class="zg-link" title="贺乾铭">贺乾铭</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3223564" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">题主永远也忘不了，那两个校服女生惊恐的眼神，和狂奔而逃的背影。<br><br><br>“真是人心不古，光天化日之下，想做点好事就这么难吗？人与人之间最基本的信任在哪里？道德底线在哪里？精神文明建设成果在哪里？”，题主紧攥着那张20块，愤怒地控诉着，扣问着。<br><br><br>“妈妈，那个叔叔怎么不穿裤子？”<br>“小孩子别多嘴！”，马路对面的妇女连拉带扯，领着孩子狂奔而逃。


</div>

</div>
